data.text:
Durable tags, labels and stickers that that stay on in the wet and in the wash!

Labels for identification

Sew-on, Iron-on or stick on Labels for Clothing, Linen, shoes, bags, food containers, water bottles, electronics, CD’s, books, pictures and anything else you can think of. Ensure that your valuable personal items are not lost in the wash, at your facility, at school or playground.

$25 for 60 Labels, $40 for 120 Labels or $50 for 200 (plus $5 package & post or collect from Beechboro near Morley if around Perth).
